{"tid":1436043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM又一社內情侶誕生「和EXO有關」！　曖昧約會背影照瘋傳","createTime":"2019-08-09T08:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T13:05:44.000Z","uid":294712,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c848d035d0cd343a30fa11c8ecf362724425853","tid":1436043,"uid":294712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"南韓近來偶像戀愛消息頻傳，「三大經紀公司」之一的SM娛樂，最近也在推特瘋傳一對「社內情侶」，不僅和天團EXO有關，甚至還出現清晰的約會背影照，在粉絲界瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n▲SM再爆一對「社內情侶」，是燦烈和世勳的愛犬－多芬和VIVI。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n不過這對SM娛樂「社內戀愛」的CP，其實不是真的偶像，而是EXO成員燦烈的愛犬「多芬」以及世勳的愛犬「VIVI」。近來有粉絲上傳黑、白二犬一起盪鞦韆的萌照，仿照「D社」的偷拍爆料照風格，並配上「SM確認VIVI和多芬正在公園約會」。<br />\n<br />\n[Breaking] SM Entertainment confirms Vivi and Toben are dating, say they are meeting in the park with good feelings <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/VZURohvckE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FVZURohvckE&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOqxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=35491331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/VZURohvckE</a><br />\n<br />\n事實上，燦烈和世勳近日組成小分隊「EXO-SC」活動，不久前才真的一起帶狗出去玩，還在IG留下認證照，因此在粉絲圈引起熱烈迴響，已經有超過2萬人轉發。粉絲笑說：「SM又一對社內戀愛！」、「如果是真的，那燦烈跟世勳就是親家了。」意外成為話題。"},{"pid":"327f912b3d3e642c956124d1addd33a2bcaa4626","tid":1436043,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"3eeebdca885c5add70d327ea816637e239182630","tid":1436043,"uid":49267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820c094b64de33721b9cbc9bbd99b9df30f075c9","tid":1436043,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"@猁狗"},{"pid":"5c63ee411e740b72552985af78b4c21b4f2e